    if ("performance" in window === false) {
      window.performance = {};
    }
    window.performance.mark = performance.mark || noop;
    window.performance.measure = performance.measure || noop;
    if ("now" in window.performance === false) {
      var nowOffset = Date.now();

        nowOffset = performance.timing.navigationStart;
      }

        return Date.now() - nowOffset;
      };
    }
  })();

<script id="wix-first-paint">
    if (window.ResizeObserver &&
        (!window.PerformanceObserver || !PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes || PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes.indexOf('paint') === -1)) {
        new ResizeObserver(function (entries, observer) {
            entries.some(function (entry) {
                var contentRect = entry.contentRect;
                if (contentRect.width > 0 && contentRect.height > 0) {
                    requestAnimationFrame(function (now) {
                        window.wixFirstPaint = now;
                        dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('wixFirstPaint'));
                    });
                    observer.disconnect();
                    return true;
                }
            });
        }).observe(document.body);
    }
</script>


<script id="scroll-bar-width-calculation">
    const div = document.createElement('div')
    div.style.overflowY = 'scroll'
    div.style.width = '50px'
    div.style.height = '50px'
    div.style.visibility = 'hidden'
    document.body.appendChild(div)
    const scrollbarWidth= div.offsetWidth - div.clientWidth
    document.body.removeChild(div)
    if(scrollbarWidth > 0){
        document.body.style.setProperty('--scrollbar-width', `${scrollbarWidth}px`)
    }
</script>

data-motion-part="BG_LAYER comp-k7ozcymg" class="if7Vw2"><div data-testid="colorUnderlay" class="tcElKx i1tH8h"></div><div id="bgMedia_comp-k7ozcymg" data-motion-part="BG_MEDIA comp-k7ozcymg" class="wG8dni"></div></div><div data-testid="columns" class="V5AUxf"><!--$--><div id="comp-k7ozcyo1" class="comp-k7ozcyo1 YzqVVZ wixui-column-strip__column"><div id="bgLayers_comp-k7ozcyo1" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><div id="comp-k7oze95v" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-k7oze95v wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_2 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:35px; line-height:normal; text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:35px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_84e06a_18c0496da2e645a59cc30e09db92406a,wf_18c0496da2e645a59cc30e09d,orig_supernatural_knight;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">For the Love of Fantasy</span></span></span></span></h2></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-jqqpkwyo" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-jqqpkwyo wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:cormorantgaramond-semibold,cormorantgaramond,cormorant garamond,serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">FOR THE LOVE OF FANTASY is part of the Monopoly Events family of pop culture conventions, attracting thousands of fans annually, our next event takes place on the weekend of 22nd-23rd August 2026 in the ExCeL London.</span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:cormorantgaramond-semibold,cormorantgaramond,cormorant garamond,serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">If you love fantasy movies and tv series then this is THE SHOW for you!</span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:cormorantgaramond-semibold,cormorantgaramond,cormorant garamond,serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">You can expect to see guests from some of these fantastic franchises! &nbsp;Lord of the Rings, Supernatural, Stranger Things, The Vampire Diaries, Harry Potter, True Blood, Fantastic Beasts, Twilight, Wednesday, The Originals, Game of Thrones, Grimm, Teen Wolf, The Sandman, Buffy The Vampire Slayer, Lucifer, Angel, Highlander, Once Upon A Time, The Chronicles of Narnia, The Lost Boys and much, much more.</span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:cormorantgaramond-semibold,cormorantgaramond,cormorant garamond,serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Expect an all star line up of actors you love, amazing interactive set and prop builds, cosplay, immersive gaming, and tens of thousands of like minded fans!</span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;"><span class="wixui-rich-text__text"></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:cormorantgaramond-semibold,cormorantgaramond,cormorant garamond,serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Transport yourself to a world of Vampires, Werewolves, wizards, orcs, witches, hobbits, demons, monsters and other supernatural favourites this summer!</span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:cormorantgaramond-semibold,cormorantgaramond,cormorant garamond,serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">To view our current guest line up for our next show, visit the <span style="text-decoration:underline;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><a href="https://www.fortheloveoffantasy.com/guests" target="_blank" class="wixui-rich-text__text">GUESTS</a></span> <script id="wix-first-paint">
    if (window.ResizeObserver &&
        (!window.PerformanceObserver || !PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes || PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes.indexOf('paint') === -1)) {
        new ResizeObserver(function (entries, observer) {
            entries.some(function (entry) {
                var contentRect = entry.contentRect;
                if (contentRect.width > 0 && contentRect.height > 0) {
                    requestAnimationFrame(function (now) {
                        window.wixFirstPaint = now;
                        dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('wixFirstPaint'));
                    });
                    observer.disconnect();
                    return true;
                }
            });
        }).observe(document.body);
    }
</script>


<script id="scroll-bar-width-calculation">
    const div = document.createElement('div')
    div.style.overflowY = 'scroll'
    div.style.width = '50px'
    div.style.height = '50px'
    div.style.visibility = 'hidden'
    document.body.appendChild(div)
    const scrollbarWidth= div.offsetWidth - div.clientWidth
    document.body.removeChild(div)
    if(scrollbarWidth > 0){
        document.body.style.setProperty('--scrollbar-width', `${scrollbarWidth}px`)
    }
</script>

data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><div id="comp-k7oze95v" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-k7oze95v wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_2 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:35px; line-height:normal; text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:35px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:wfont_84e06a_18c0496da2e645a59cc30e09db92406a,wf_18c0496da2e645a59cc30e09d,orig_supernatural_knight;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">For the Love of Fantasy</span></span></span></span></h2></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-jqqpkwyo" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-jqqpkwyo wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:cormorantgaramond-semibold,cormorantgaramond,cormorant garamond,serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">FOR THE LOVE OF FANTASY is part of the Monopoly Events family of pop culture conventions, attracting thousands of fans annually, our next event takes place on the weekend of 22nd-23rd August 2026 in the ExCeL London.</span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:cormorantgaramond-semibold,cormorantgaramond,cormorant garamond,serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">If you love fantasy movies and tv series then this is THE SHOW for you!</span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:cormorantgaramond-semibold,cormorantgaramond,cormorant garamond,serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">You can expect to see guests from some of these fantastic franchises! &nbsp;Lord of the Rings, Supernatural, Stranger Things, The Vampire Diaries, Harry Potter, True Blood, Fantastic Beasts, Twilight, Wednesday, The Originals, Game of Thrones, Grimm, Teen Wolf, The Sandman, Buffy The Vampire Slayer, Lucifer, Angel, Highlander, Once Upon A Time, The Chronicles of Narnia, The Lost Boys and much, much more.</span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:cormorantgaramond-semibold,cormorantgaramond,cormorant garamond,serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Expect an all star line up of actors you love, amazing interactive set and prop builds, cosplay, immersive gaming, and tens of thousands of like minded fans!</span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;"><span class="wixui-rich-text__text"></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:cormorantgaramond-semibold,cormorantgaramond,cormorant garamond,serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Transport yourself to a world of Vampires, Werewolves, wizards, orcs, witches, hobbits, demons, monsters and other supernatural favourites this summer!</span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:20px; text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:20px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:cormorantgaramond-semibold,cormorantgaramond,cormorant garamond,serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">To view our current guest line up for our next show, visit the <span style="text-decoration:underline;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><a href="https://www.fortheloveoffantasy.com/guests" target="_blank" class="wixui-rich-text__text">GUESTS</a></span> page.</span></span></span></p></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--></div></section><!--/$--></div></div></section><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--></div></div></div></div></main><footer 			const wixAdsOffsetHeight = document.getElementById('WIX_ADS')?.offsetHeight || 0;
			const header = document.getElementsByTagName('header')[0];

			let headerOffsetHeight = 0;

			if (header) {
				const headerPosition = window.getComputedStyle(header).getPropertyValue('position').toLowerCase();
				const isHeaderStickyOrFixed = headerPosition === 'sticky' || headerPosition === 'fixed';
				headerOffsetHeight = isHeaderStickyOrFixed ? header.offsetHeight : 0;
			}

			document.documentElement.style.scrollPaddingTop = `${wixAdsOffsetHeight + headerOffsetHeight}px`;
